---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Nick Battaglia"
  description="JD/MBA candidate at Indiana University Maurer School of Law and Kelley School of Business, building at the intersection of law, finance, and technology."
>

  <section class="container pt-20 pb-16 max-w-2xl">
    <p class="pill mb-5">About</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light text-text mb-8 leading-tight">
      Law, finance,<br/>and technology.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-5 text-text-dim leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm a dual J.D./M.B.A. candidate at Indiana University's Maurer School
        of Law and Kelley School of Business (Class of 2029). I'm a Stewart
        Fellow and Elmore Scholar at Maurer, where I serve as President of the
        Data, AI &amp; Technology Association and am an associate of the IP
        Theory journal.
      </p>
      <p>
        My legal interests center on the intersection of technology, data
        privacy, and finance &mdash; including regulatory policy for AI/ML
        systems, digital assets, capital markets, and information privacy.
        Prior to law school I worked at Acrelec doing data science, QA, and
        product management work; I hold a Series 65 license and a Microsoft
        Azure Fundamentals certification.
      </p>
      <p>
        This summer (2026), I'll work with OPLGunnerCooke's LegalTech and
        data privacy groups in Budapest as part of the Stewart Fellows Program.
        Outside of my coursework, I built <a href="/projects/lawagent" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-strong">Argus</a>
        &mdash; an M&amp;A drafting and review assistant powered by a Corrective
        RAG pipeline on Vertex Gemini 2.5 Flash, Cohere Embed v4 and Rerank 3.5,
        and Neon pgvector &mdash; designed to surface issues in complex contracts
        while keeping sensitive content under a Flash-Lite anonymization layer
        that prevents unscrubbed text from ever reaching the LLM.
      </p>
      <p>
        I grew up on Chicago's Northwest Side and am committed to building my
        career there. I graduated from the University of Iowa's Tippie College
        of Business in 2024 with a B.B.A. in Business Analytics and Information
        Systems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Education</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text font-medium">Indiana University</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">Maurer School of Law &mdash; J.D.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">Kelley School of Business &mdash; M.B.A.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim mt-2">University of Iowa &mdash; B.B.A., Business Analytics &amp; Information Systems</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Expected 2029 (J.D./M.B.A.) &middot; 2024 (B.B.A.)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Focus areas</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
          {['Legal AI', 'M&A', 'Data privacy', 'Digital assets', 'Capital markets', 'AI/ML policy'].map(area => (
            <span class="pill">{area}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-5 mb-2">Credentials</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="pill">Series 65</span>
          <span class="pill">Azure AZ-900</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
